citation: Proclamation under the Public Health Amendment (Cervical Screening) Act 2009 (Tas)
text:
Proclamation under the Public Health Amendment (Cervical Screening) Act 2009

I, the Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, by this my proclamation made under section 2 of the Public Health Amendment (Cervical Screening) Act 2009 fix 1 January 2010 as the day on which that Act commences.

14 December 2009

PETER G. UNDERWOOD

Governor

By His Excellency's Command,

LARA GIDDINGS

Minister for Health

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 23 December 2009

This proclamation is administered in the Department of Health and Human Services.
